div.div: Download feature not working within update panel in asp.net

You cannot return an attachment in an UpdatePanel partial postback, since the results are used by the ScriptManager to update a DIV (not the whole response). The simplest fix for what you're trying to do would be to make your download button as a postback control. That would cause that button to initiate a full postback. Here's the code below to include in your Page_Load ScriptManager.GetCurrent(this.Page).RegisterPostBackControl(this.lnkDownload);
